{"tid":1150423,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞和街水果店雪櫃短路起火　逾百居民疏散","createTime":"2019-05-11T22:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T07:32:45.000Z","uid":247610,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"95288b29675c6951c82ca560c8b49786b94b250f","tid":1150423,"uid":247610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T22:21:45.000Z","msg":"今晚(11日)8時許，觀塘瑞和街42號地下一間已關門的水果店門外，有途人發現有雜物起火，冒出大量濃煙，慌忙報警求助，附近大廈逾百名居民亦走到樓下安全地方暫避。消防接報趕至，出動2隊煙帽隊及開動2條喉灌救，約半小時後將火救熄，火警中一名消防員受輕傷，由救護車送往聯合醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n事後水果店付之一炬，大量水果燒焦，雜物散落一地，由於火勢蔓延迅速，水果店樓上一單位外牆及冷氣機亦熏黑損毀，該單位2名住客得悉火警發生後，趕返現場向警員了解。消防經初步調查後，相信水果店內一部雪櫃短路，有火舌燒着雜物引致火警，女負責人其後返回現場助查。受火警影響，介乎瑞寧街至輔仁街一段瑞和街一度暫時封閉，行人及車輛需繞道而行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190511/bkn-20190511205237010-0511_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3b7n-rmBXW2B7ROQZa_vvY5_AZma85siytEDmPdDdeu8-L-xmwAGVdmVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190511%2Fbkn-20190511205237010-0511_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3b7n-rmBXW2B7ROQZa_vvY5_AZma85siytEDmPdDdeu8-L-xmwAGVdmVs&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNWzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=1eac0a91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190511/bkn-20190511205237010-0511_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3b7n-rmBXW2B7ROQZa_vvY5_AZma85siytEDmPdDdeu8-L-xmwAGVdmVs</a><br />\n<br />\n點解瑞和街成日都有事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbebfaa54ebd307402f30ed26780f385f586f14c","tid":1150423,"uid":38189,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T22:49:39.000Z","msg":"😏"},{"pid":"a53576b2d1b054438f2217e3a759fe2535917aaa","tid":1150423,"uid":124020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cbebfaa54ebd307402f30ed26780f385f586f14c","tid":1150423,"uid":38189,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T22:49:39.000Z","msg":"😏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T23:08:25.000Z","msg":