nk target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/866940</a><br />\n<br />\n[全港最平] 瑞和街 橙售價為12元3個、菜心每斤9元，而生菜為5元一斤<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/912860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/912860</a>"},{"pid":"1ebccae81e47c8da7021be5298624a13393fb061","tid":1150423,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"係咪冇交保護費俾N賓"}]}